During the first week or so Velious was out, I was often the only 49+ or 56+ cleric to be found in the EW-GD-Kael area.  Thus I got a HUUUUUUGE number of tells from people.  This problem is basically gone now.  The infusion of epics and younger clerics on their way up has basically cured this problem for me.<br>
